title: [Boreas Hills, Etesian Terrace]
description: Water trickles down from the mountain above, gently cascading into a pond here before continuing its way through the hills in the form of a small stream.  Houses sit around the pond, small paths leading from them to the main road.  A small wooden bridge continues the roadway over the stream.
